{"about_the_game":"&quot;Sugar,sugar,sugarcoat&quot; is a dating simulation game set in a school. Interact with the girls and gain their love. You must then offer that love to the devil you love.<br><br><strong>system</strong><br>You can read the story with a click. There are also options within the story, and the story changes depending on what you choose.<br><br><br><strong>story</strong><br>Your character,  &quot;Helena&quot;,  has been cursed by a girl named &quot;Marie&quot;, who calls herself the devil. Helena, who loves Marie, decides to give her love as Marie asked. (Whether or not that was Helena's own will.)<br>The characters &quot;Clarice,&quot; &quot;Michelle,&quot; and &quot;Sarah&quot; are Helena's closest friends. Talk to them and generate love to offer to the devil.<br><br><br><strong>characters</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722200/extras/chara_cl.png?t=1733281819\" /><br><br>Clarice: She appears to be serious, but in fact she is a frivolous girl. Her free-spirited behavior is conspicuous, but there are also glimpses of a kind-hearted side.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722200/extras/chara_mi.png?t=1733281819\" /><br><br>Michelle: A friendly girl with a sunny smile. She likes pretty, soft and sweet things, and her expression changes often.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722200/extras/chara_sa.png?t=1733281819\" /><br><br>Sarah: A girl who always smiles peacefully. She takes pleasure in helping others and has a heart of compassion for all things.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722200/extras/chara_he.png?t=1733281819\" /><br><br>Helena: She is a serious girl with limited emotional expression. She is hard to recognize at first glance, but she cares